OL,7,FI first interviewed Betty Brown back
OL,8,Fin January 2024.
OL,10,FI knew immediately upon meeting her
OL,11,Fhow fiercely determined she was to
OL,12,Fensure she received redress for years
OL,13,Fof suffering inflicted upon her, her
OL,14,Flate husband Oswall and her family by
OL,15,Ffaulty Horizon software installed in
OL,16,Ftheir Post Office in Annfield Plain in
OL,17,FCounty Durham.
