OL,7,FHer husband died before seeing a penny
OL,8,Fpaid back and Betty still believes the
OL,9,Fstress of being wrongly accused
OL,10,Fcontributed to his death.
OL,12,FI wanted to catch up with Betty
OL,13,Fknowing she was in the final stages of
OL,14,Freceiving her recompense from a post
OL,15,Foffice compensation scheme. It was in
OL,16,Fresearching what we would talk about
OL,17,Fthat I stumbled across a fact: The
OL,18,FNorth East not only has the oldest
OL,19,Fvictim of the Horizon scandal, but
OL,20,Falso the youngest too.
