OL,3,CInside the meeting of two Post Office
OL,4,Cscandal victims we helped bring
OL,5,Ctogether
OL,7,FEnter Chris Head. He was just 18 years
OL,8,Fold when he became Britain's youngest
OL,9,Fsub-postmaster, taking over his local
OL,10,FWest Bolden branch near Sunderland. In
OL,11,F2014, his Horizon system ran up
OL,12,Fshortfalls of around #88,000.
OL,14,FHe was pursued by the Post Office
OL,15,Fthrough the Civil Courts for cash they
OL,16,Fclaimed he owed them. His reputation
OL,17,Fruined, he says himself he struggled
OL,18,Fto find work at home and ended up
OL,19,Fmoving abroad because of the damage to
OL,20,Fhis reputation. He eventually settled
OL,21,Fin Greece, where he still lives now.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
