OL,7,FFor Betty more than two decades have
OL,8,Fpassed since her fight for justice
OL,9,Fbegan. Next year will be two decades
OL,10,Fsince Chris took over his branch in
OL,11,FWest Boldon.
OL,13,FFive years ago he led a petition
OL,14,Fcalling for a public inquiry into the
OL,15,Fscandal and has campaigned tirelessly
OL,16,Fon behalf of sub-postmasters since.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
