OL,3,CInside the meeting of two Post Office
OL,4,Cscandal victims we helped bring
OL,5,Ctogether
OL,7,FBoth Betty and Chris have unique
OL,8,Fperspectives on the scandal. I knew we
OL,9,Fhad to get them together. If only to
OL,10,Fhear their united voices, continuing
OL,11,Fto campaign for justice. Not just for
OL,12,Fthemselves, but for the thousands of
OL,13,Fother sub-postmasters affected by the
OL,14,Fscandal.
OL,16,FBut despite shared trauma, they had
OL,17,Fnever met. Never been in the same room
OL,18,Ftogether. Never been on TV together.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
