OL,3,CInside the meeting of two Post Office
OL,4,Cscandal victims we helped bring
OL,5,Ctogether
OL,7,FIn the end, the logistics were easy -
OL,8,Fboth were desperate to meet one
OL,9,Fanother and within a matter of weeks,
OL,10,FChris was flying home, back to the
OL,11,FNorth East to meet Betty.
OL,13,FWe arranged to film with the pair at a
OL,14,Fhome belonging to one of Betty's
OL,15,Ffamily. I wasn't sure how that moment
OL,16,Fwhen they first locked eyes would be.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
