OL,3,CInside the meeting of two Post Office
OL,4,Cscandal victims we helped bring
OL,5,Ctogether
OL,7,FThey spoke at length about how they
OL,8,Ffelt finally meeting one another,
OL,9,Ftheir shared pain, their hope that
OL,10,Fthose sub-postmasters still waiting
OL,11,Ffor redress can be paid quickly and
OL,12,Fwhat their messages are for those
OL,13,Fstill campaigning for justice.
OL,15,FIt was emotional, it was powerful and
OL,16,FBetty and Chris hope it helps shine a
OL,17,Flight on a scandal that has shocked
OL,18,Fnot just those in the North East but
OL,19,Faround the country, too.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
