OL,4,Cscandal victims we helped bring
OL,5,Ctogether
OL,7,FThey say they won't give up fighting
OL,8,Funtil every last sub-postmaster has
OL,9,Fhad their claim settled.
OL,11,FHearing the passion in their voices,
OL,12,Fseeing the determination on their
OL,13,Ffaces and knowing what they've
OL,14,Fachieved in their fight for justice so
OL,15,Ffar, it would be foolish not to
OL,16,Fbelieve them.
